race.description: Book Function Centre 4 Functions QTIS 3YO Mdn Hcp
race.comment: MILK MAID (4) returns today after a five-month spell that would have done her the world of good. She is stronger now, and a recent trial win suggests she's ready to rumble. Follow the market leads. OUTCRY (7) showed early speed when resuming last start but peaked late to fourth over 1100m at this track just over 6 weeks ago. She should improve with that run under her belt, and can figure in the top 3 here. BETTER STORM (3) comes back from a five-and-a-half-month break after finishing sixth over 1300m here last time out in the spring. A recent fourth in a Rockhampton trial has her ready, and she is worth including in all top 4 combos. BELVEDERE MISS (2) makes her debut, and with the blinkers on, she can figure in the top 4. Watch for any positive market leads.
